{"tid":1026084,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(痴撚線)英國人窮到連插頭電線都偷","createTime":"2019-02-17T23:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T03:14:56.000Z","uid":12972,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c4e4676afa9b51bce2722a3820e6b4d945a2e1","tid":1026084,"uid":12972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T23:23:59.000Z","msg":"小弟去英國exchange  第一次撘train去旅行<br />\n撘撘下有個西女人問我借iphone叉電器<br />\n我見佢電話冇乜電  但又好似好急周圍問人借<br />\n一時心軟借咗條iphone線比佢  仲借埋個插蘇比佢<br />\n真係算唔話得<br />\n過咗個幾鐘  咪話電話  我相信佢個人都應該叉足電<br />\n屌佢老母 <br />\n唔止個iphone線唔撚見咗  連個八婆都唔撚見埋<br />\n聽過歐洲啲仆街好撚鍾意偷嘢 <br />\n估唔到apple條濕鳩線同插頭都要偷<br />\n奉勸咁多位巴打咪撚借嘢比啲西女人"},{"pid":"34edec84c5a288fbdb0463087634dd6951b1a034","tid":1026084,"uid":40470,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T23:26:16.000Z","msg":"樓主以為有西屌所以先借<br />\n<br />\n果一個鐘完全浸淫起性幻想之中<br />\n<br />\n射左四次"},{"pid":"bbbc828087f318abc17ecf150e1a815597d33bc3","tid":1026084,"uid":12972,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"34edec84c5a288fbdb0463087634dd6951b1a034","tid":1026084,"uid":40470,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T23:26:16.000Z","msg":"樓主以為有西屌所以先借<br />\n<br />\n果一個鐘完全浸淫起性幻想之中<br />\n<br />\n射左四次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T23:32:31.000Z","msg":"西女人=鬼婆=/=鬼妹<br />\n我唔是耆齡王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da17be4c6de0e7dde3fd5f35e78201b4599b2051","tid":1026084,"uid":160054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T23:45:40.000Z","msg":"用一條iPhone線同插蘇換一個鐘頭性幻想<br />\n抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df51a00265a073825cad42f6d7a6df0c4d8457d8","tid":1026084,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T23:52:15.000Z","msg":"做兄弟果時都借左條線比化妝師一去無回頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過條女幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gi